      <div class="w-full text-center lg:text-end">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">
          Problems Caused by Not Preheating Low-Cost Fuels
        </h2><br />
        <p class="text-grisT text-lg md:text-xl">
          Low-cost fuels that are not preheated cause and intensify the
          following serious problems:
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="lg:w-4/5 bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 self-center text-sm lg:text-lg md:text-lg text-grisT flex justify-center"
      >
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
          <li>Unburned microdroplets lead to a significant waste of fuel</li>
          <li>The hot-mix becomes contaminated with unburned fuel</li>
          <li>
            This contamination causes the asphalt pavement to have a much
            shorter service life
          </li>
          <li>
            Additionally, the atmosphere is polluted by gases from incomplete
            combustion
          </li>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
            <li>
              Paying environmental fees for operating polluting equipment.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="w-full bg-[url(src/assets/images/IntegralAsphalt/Hero1.webp)] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat my-10"
  >
    <div class="w-full bg-black/70 py-10 md:py-20 bg-cover h-full">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto items-center px-8">
        <ul class="text-white text-lg lg:text-2xl md:text-2xl space-y-5">
          <li>
            Only brands with cutting-edge technology offer preheaters, usually
            as an expensive add-on option.
          </li>
          <li>
            Since 2014, Triaso includes preheaters in all of its drum
            models—Parallel Flow and Counterflow—as standard equipment, with no
            extra cost.
          </li>
          <li>
            This is part of our effort to reduce pollution and extend the
            lifespan of roadways.
          </li>
          <li>
            We believe that these types of actions are the best investment.
          </li>
        </ul>
